eses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Redis操作HGET从正常1739.7ms激增至77555ms，延迟倍数44.6倍，是最严重的延迟瓶颈\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-0和cartservice-1实例的延迟显著增加：cartservice-0从2495.9ms增至78209ms（31.3倍），cartservice-1从2622.3ms增至33579.5ms（12.8倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice内部调用CartService/GetCart从8686.5ms增至35456.9ms（4.1倍），ShippingService/GetQuote从9347.6ms增至40463.3ms（4.3倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend的CartService/AddItem从5216.3ms增至40210ms（7.7倍），但部分操作如CartService/GetCart显示延迟下降\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析\n\n### 延迟瓶颈识别\n1. **Redis是根因服务**：HGET操作延迟增加44.6倍，是所有服务中最严重的延迟\n2. **cartservice受影响最严重**：作为Redis的直接调用方，cartservice的两个实例都出现显著延迟\n3. **调用链传播路径**：redis → cartservice → checkoutservice/frontend\n\n### 异常模式分析\n- **最下游异常**：redis是调用链的最底层，其异常导致上游服务连锁反应\n- **错误传播**：从数据库层(redis)向上传播到业务层(cartservice)再到前端层\n- **部分服务正常**：productcatalogservice和shippingservice延迟相对较小，说明故障集中在购物车相关功能\n\n当前处于初始扫描阶段，已识别出redis作为潜在的根因组件，需要进一步分析错误状态码和具体错误类型来确认根因。", "metric_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"cpu_usage\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased significantly from 2995.0 to 3031.0 (median_change_ratio: 0.0119, p99_change_ratio: 1.6748)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: normal_median=2995.0, fault_median=3031.0, normal_p99=5315.52, fault_p99=60059.9\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max increased from 3649.0 to 3776.0 (median_change_ratio: 0.0342, p99_change_ratio: 1.6248)\",\n      \"evidence\"